curam.util.type

Class FrequencyPattern.DayOfMonth

  • java.lang.Object
    • curam.util.type.FrequencyPattern.DayOfMonth
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    FrequencyPattern

    public static final class FrequencyPattern.DayOfMonth
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    An enumerated type used in the interface to FrequencyPattern to indicate the day of month. Values can be 0-31, or one of a set of "special" values that indicate the first, second, third, fourth, or last of a particular day of week in the month.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
